{"tid":2099842,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"參考 Apple 使用 ARM 處理器   大陸電腦使用華為「鯤鵬」處理器 賣7500蚊","createTime":"2020-07-08T14:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T01:23:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5d0608dba6c0e1c2b48e3744c6a51db25a3a37","tid":2099842,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/nb/img/2020-07/07/27263/uniqlo_1_460a46e4b91bdbcb964d6e314c334b32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fnb%2Fimg%2F2020-07%2F07%2F27263%2Funiqlo_1_460a46e4b91bdbcb964d6e314c334b32.png&h=2618ed0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前 Apple 在 WWDC20 宣佈 Mac 電腦會陸續改用自家處理器，據說有大陸廠商亦打算有樣學樣，在桌面電腦使用 ARM 架構的處理器。近日有 YouTube 頻道購入一部桌面電腦，裡面採用的正正是華為旗下 HiSilicon 的鯤鵬 920 處理器。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有傳華為打算將原本為伺服器而設的 7nm 製程鯤鵬處理器，應用到消費級桌面電腦系統，現在終於有真機在網上曝光。這部電腦配備 ARM v8 的鯤鵬 920 八核處理器，直接焊接在華為 D920S10 桌面電腦底板上，作業系統則是基於 Linux 的 64-bit UOS。底板有 4x DIMM 插槽，但只搭配 16GB DDR4-2666 RAM。電腦內安裝了一塊 Yeston RX550 顯示卡，可以支援 4K 解像度和 60Hz 更新率。<br />\n<br />\n別以為使用華為的處理器就會令售價變得便宜，這部桌面電腦花了該 YouTube 頻道 7,500 人民幣（折合 HK$8,280），然而要使用 UOS 的軟件商店，用戶需要先支付 800 人民幣（約 HK$884）將系統開通，但裡面的軟件數量和種類乏善足陳，相信無法應付專業的應用。YouTuber 以 Blender BMW 測試渲染能力，結果花了 11 分 47 秒完成，比起同代的桌面電腦處理器都慢了一截。"},{"pid":"98cdb8e942ff2f3168b49d2e890fa63d44f181ce","tid":2099842,"uid":292497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"but can it blend?"},{"pid":"afd13a6a2e5ba15194e610931e0a6856697b3012","tid":2099842,"uid":54721,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"昆鳩處理器"},{"pid":"7ab0c4951124670c5f7c575733231b72603f9b79","tid":2099842,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1143/27263/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1143%2F27263%2F1%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=d9826da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1143/27263/1/</a>"},{"pid":"a464032067ed418aaf66e2ad255d06cc01e893bf","tid":2099842,"uid":299514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"無windows無google可以做啲乜？"},{"pid":"f378239b190b43b8d98c0df3720992137331bc51","tid":2099842,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:28:40.000Z","msg":"鬥地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbc608c3bcf33fbfe405097005186acf8441259","tid":2099842,"uid":257491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a464032067ed418aaf66e2ad255d06cc01e893bf","tid":2099842,"uid":299514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"無windows無google可以做啲乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"做數"},{"pid":"986fd20c22806a378edc058bf3c4da376e8be9ec","tid":2099842,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDZmmpq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDZmmpq.png&h=c2972e9a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nIO只有VGA, 2 UBS2.0, 2 USB 3.0<br />\nHDMI? DVI 唔需要咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6da480f9b234ad0f4a5f5e91ca28c7d1dfad32","tid":2099842,"uid":8880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"server cpu仲廢撚過家用cpu?"},{"pid":"652a5b48770cc93962ea2b02613f40e4c1cd0fa5","tid":2099842,"uid":48064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"986fd20c22806a378edc058bf3c4da376e8be9ec","tid":2099842,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDZmmpq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDZmmpq.png&h=c2972e9